      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAILATA (4) has a strong record this track and trip with seven wins and four placings from 19 starts. Hit the frame latest (27.59) when second at Mandurah in a Free For All. Rates on top and should go close. FERNDALE FLYER (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (37.82) last time in a Grade 5 at Mandurah. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from five starts. Expected to give a good account. SHEERAN MELODY (1) is a talented dog who is a winner of seven races but missed the frame last time when fifth at Mandurah (23.44). Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from four starts. Should play a prominent role. PAM KEEPING (6) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
